snippet.title: John Candy: I Like Me - Official Teaser Trailer (2025) Documentary
snippet.description:
Don't miss the Teaser Trailer for John Candy: I Like Me, a new documentary film distributed by Amazon Prime Video. Viewers can explore the life of the Canadian comedic icon John Candy when John Candy: I Like Me streams on October 10 exclusively on Amazon Prime Video.

This John Candy film documents his on- and off-camera existence, featuring never-before-seen home videos, intimate access to his family, and candid recollections from collaborators to paint a bigger picture of one of the brightest stars of the ’70s, ’80s, and ’90s. It’s the story of a son, husband, father, friend, and professional driven to bring joy to audiences and loved ones while battling personal ghosts and Hollywood pressures. 

John Candy: I Like Me stars Tom Hanks, Bill Murray, Steve Martin, Conan O'Brien, and more. The documentary is directed by Colin Hanks. 

John Candy: I Like Me streams on October 10 exclusively on Amazon Prime Video.

snippet.description:
Khalsa Raj is a cinematic retelling inspired by the life and legacy of Maharaja Ranjit Singh, the legendary Sher-e-Punjab who united the land, protected the faith, and built one of Asia’s most powerful empires.

This film has been created with utmost respect for Sikh history, Punjabi culture, and the spirit of Khalsa Raj. While based on historical events, this is a creative cinematic interpretation.


❤️ Why This Film Matters:
This project was created with immense hard work and dedication to bring the story of Maharaja Ranjit Singh to life for our Punjabi community and for audiences worldwide. Creating at this scale is not easy — but it is done out of love for our history, pride in our culture, and respect for our ancestors.

AI Production By : Athink AI Studios ( https://www.instagram.com/athink_aistudios/ )

⚔️ Who Was Maharaja Ranjit Singh?
 • The Lion of Punjab, who turned scars into steel.
 • A visionary leader who united Sikhs, Hindus, Muslims, and Christians in one kingdom.
 • A warrior who stopped invaders and built an empire that stood strong for decades.
 • A patron who bathed the Golden Temple in gold, leaving behind an eternal legacy.

⸻
Important Note:
Some visuals, faces, and representations in this project have been created or enhanced using Artificial Intelligence (AI) technologies. This means certain facial features or appearances may not be exact replicas of real historical figures. This work does not claim to be a documentary or an absolute historical account — it is a work of respect, imagination, and inspiration.

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: Minecraft Speedrunner Swap VS 2 Hunters
snippet.description:
This was crazy intense. Manhunt, but with a twist.

This video, I teamed up with a Manhunt PRO, Baablu, in a new #MinecraftManhunt challenge. We have to speedrun and beat Minecraft against two hunters, but we swap who is playing every minute! It was hilarious and super intense.

Follow my socials:
➽ Twitter - @dreamwastaken
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dreampublic


In this challenge Baablu and I essentially are one player. We share an inventory, health, position, and basically everything else. The idea is that we are swapping who has control of one player. When we are swapped out, we don't know what is happening at all. We see a black screen and hear nothing.

We decided to have the hunters be one hunter from my videos and one hunter from his videos! This is one of my first ever collabs of this type, if you'd like to see more, like the video!

This was played on Minecraft 1.21.8, and is a custom coded challenge. There were a few bugs that we plan to iron out before we try something like this again!

200,000 likes for me to try this challenge with someone else!


Baablu: @Baablu 
BadBoyHalo: @thesaintsofgames 
Fantst: @Fantst 

Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/DreamWasTaken
